            <note xml:id="foot.f2">George later published on ripple marks (<ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_11301.xml" resp="#automat" cert="low">G. H. Darwin 1883</ref>; see <ref target="./DCP-LETT-12828.xml">letter from G. H. Darwin, 19 November 1880</ref> and n. 4).</note>
